'''Qwasi Blay Jnr.''', ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Gana]] <ref>https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/entertainment/Get-familiar-with-Ghanaian-most-wanted-actor-Qwasi-Blay-837322</ref>.  Azwi cyane kubera uruhare rwe muri firime ''Adoma'' na ''Grilled''<ref>https://www.thefamousnaija.com/2021/03/qwasi-blay-jnr-biography-age-pictures.html</ref> . Yagaragaye muri firime cumi neshanu na seri enye za TV<ref>https://sw.dokument.pp.ua/search/1?kw=1&q=quasi%20blay%20jr.</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Yavukiye muri [[Gana]] nk'umwana wa gatatu mu muryango ufite barumuna be batanu: abagabo bane n'umugore.<ref>https://www.thefamousnaija.com/2021/03/qwasi-blay-jnr-biography-age-pictures.html</ref> Yarangije amashuri abanza n'ayisumbuye muri Great Lamptey Mills. Hanyuma yakomereje amashuri muri Aburi Secondary Technical (SHS)<ref>https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/entertainment/Get-familiar-with-Ghanaian-most-wanted-actor-Qwasi-Blay-837322</ref>. Amashuri makuru yayize muri kaminuza ya tekinike ya Koforidua ahabwa impamyabumenyi ihanitse (HND) mu kugura no gutanga.<ref>https://blakkpepper.com/2020/01/all-you-need-to-know-about-actor-qwasi-blay-jr-alias-most-wanted/</ref>  

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga wo gukina mu 2016 akiri umwana, agaragara muri ''Gray Dust'', ''Grilled'', na serial ''Deju Vu'' <ref>https://beeniewords.com/5-things-you-need-to-know-about-ghanaian-most-wanted-actor-qwasi-blay-jnr/</ref>.  Yahawe Best Entertainment Male honor at the tertiary level and best male entertainment act at the maiden edition of the Social Media Entertainment awards.<ref>https://www.peacefmonline.com/pages/showbiz/movies/201912/397770.php</ref>  Nyuma yaje gutorwa nk'umukinnyi witwaye neza mu mwanya wa mbere mu nshuro ya 9 ya [[Gana]] Movie Awards kubera uruhare muri filime ''Adoma'' <ref>https://stories.showmax.com/the-rich-girl-ghana-series/</ref>.    

